{"tid":2142090,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人multitasking好廢？","createTime":"2020-08-06T07:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T10:14:21.000Z","uid":239146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8cbcdad3f916d3108d89b5012ef32b165e3dc8f","tid":2142090,"uid":239146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"我成日做做下A俾老闆叫左我做BCDEF<br />\n之後就唔會記得做A 或者啲野會錯晒 <br />\n犯啲底級錯誤 有啲on9 typo<br />\n我做野果陣連聽歌/電台都唔得<br />\n由細到大做同一時間只可以專心做一兩件事<br />\n考dse就考dse 上莊就上莊<br />\n專心做一件事 出黎outcome都通常above mean<br />\n不過一分身做好多樣野 就樣樣收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2479256fb67c44d10498a9136042e0ea33b725","tid":2142090,"uid":15984,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"multitasking = prioritize 再 single task"},{"pid":"6f64046ec3f17d85d5c2ff745806e2c9c04d28cd","tid":2142090,"uid":62318,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ae2479256fb67c44d10498a9136042e0ea33b725","tid":2142090,"uid":15984,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"multitasking = prioritize 再 single task"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"依個只係multitasking唔好既解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過樓主可學下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652479aef9b965101f89c7abcaa3ecf928db3425","tid":2142090,"uid":239146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae2479256fb67c44d10498a9136042e0ea33b725","tid":2142090,"uid":15984,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"multitasking = prioritize 再 single task"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"都啱 我諗我係prioritize後再single task果陣出事<br />\n做緊task A又會心思思諗task BCDEF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30b792cfd6ded393b103be1c6d74daa644aa5b7","tid":2142090,"uid":34060,"like":4,"dis